{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"268","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"企業可在公廁做廣告！環保署推新版公廁認養","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>環保署今天召開「公廁促進<a href='https://udn.com/search/tagging/2/%E8%AA%8D%E9%A4%8A' rel='103711' style='color: rgb(0, 84, 166); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none;'><span style='color: rgb(136, 136, 136); text-decoration-line: underline;'>認養</span></a>計畫說明會」，推出公廁認養新模式，讓企業可在公廁結合<a href='https://udn.com/search/tagging/2/%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A' rel='127644' style='color: rgb(0, 84, 166); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none;'><span style='color: rgb(136, 136, 136); text-decoration-line: underline;'>廣告</span></a>，宣傳品牌，減少公務支出。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>環保署表示，希望企業認養公廁，結合更多資源，建構優質的公廁，提供民眾更潔淨舒適的如廁空間。而企業透過認養公廁，回饋社會，提升企業社會責任正面形象；公部門得以減少公廁管理維護支出，為公、私部門及社會大眾創造三贏的局面。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>環保署長李應元表示，公<a href='https://udn.com/search/tagging/2/%E5%BB%81%E6%89%80' rel='134703' style='color: rgb(0, 84, 166); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none;'><span style='color: rgb(136, 136, 136); text-decoration-line: underline;'>廁所</span></a>在地往往是地方人潮聚集之處。德國瓦爾公司(Wall)在柏林締造公廁結合企業廣告行銷的成功經驗，讓公廁不僅止於廁所功能，還能化身成為兼具廣告收益的賺錢金雞母，達到企業廣告宣傳效果，如此形成正向循環，達到優質公廁的永續經營模式。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>環保署表示，以往公廁認養模式多以環境巡檢為主。去年，公廁認養試辦期，媒合國內知名衛生紙廠商認養台北市立大學中正堂公廁，由免費提供衛生紙、洗手乳等自家產品，將公廁營造成品牌宣傳與產品體驗地點，提升企業形象。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>環保署表示，打造優質公廁需要企業熱情參與，藉由說明會，鼓勵國內企業參與公廁促進認養計畫，提升公廁潔淨品質，攜手打造潔淨舒適的如廁空間，提升我國優質公廁的形象。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>資料來源:https://udn.com/news/story/7266/3104735</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2018-05-14","clk_count":"264"}}